URL = https://www.thecommonsproject.org/


=Description=

"The Commons Project’s mission is to build digital platforms and services that put people’s interests first.  We want platforms that are safe, respectful, and serve the goals of better health, increased civic participation, access to knowledge, and financial inclusion. 

We believe that solving these problems the right way demands a new type of organization. Our non-profit structure brings together mission driven investors and entrepreneurial teams to deliver best in class technology free from third party financial interests."


=Example=

"working with UC San Francisco, Cornell Tech, Sage Bionetworks and Open mHealth to pilot CommonHealth, an app for people to collect, store, and share their health data with trusted partners."


